Generate a monthly breakdown of goals for the transition from {{ current_role }} to {{ target_role }} over {{ estimated_duration_months }} months.

Roadmap Phases:
{% for phase in roadmap_phases %}
Phase {{ phase.phase_number }}: {{ phase.title }}
Duration: {{ phase.duration }}
Description: {{ phase.description }}
{% endfor %}

Construct a monthly plan. Return only a JSON object:
{
  "monthly_milestones": [
    {
      "month_number": 1,
      "milestone": "Monthly milestone focus"
    }
  ]
}

Ensure the response contains only the raw, valid JSON object. Do not add markdown backticks, notes, or explanations.
